<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Yes, AN is a valid Scrabble word in both TWL and SOWPODS, worth 2 points. While the score seems modest, AN is one of the most strategically versatile 2-letter words because of its incredible hook potential — it can be front-hooked with nearly every consonant in the alphabet to form valid 3-letter words.</p>

